title: Bert Forgot To Tell His Fiancée Strangers Were Staying In Their House
description:
Bert's best friend is coming to visit and he made not one, but TWO mistakes. First, he completely for got to tell his fiancée literal STRANGERS were coming to stay with them, and then he got something ELSE totally messed up which threw off his whole morning!
